    "Finally, in order to assess chatbots' answers consistency, all questions were repeated three times, and possible changes in surgical suggestions were collected.In addition, three senior glaucoma specialists (G.G., A.B., and S.R.)",
    "were asked to analyze the same 66 cases and to define a shared surgical choice.",
    "Cohen coefficient analysis was used to ensure that the concordance was at least 0.90.",
    "If all three operators agreed, the ideal surgical treatment for that specific case was identified.",
